      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so quiet here. i keep expecting to hear him in the kitchen or the sound of his keys in the door but there's nothing. the house just feels empty and heavy. i don't know how people go on living like this. it feels like the world just stopped turning and i'm the only one left in the dark.",
